eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.EyaDefDocument
IEC 61400-15-2 EYA DEF top-level data model.
Attributes: json_uri (Optional[str]): Unique URI of the JSON document. Default is None. title (str): Title of the energy assessment report. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. project_name (str): Name of the project under assessment. project_county (str): Country where the project under assessment is located. document_id (Optional[str]): The ID of the report document; not including the version when 'document_version' is used. Default is None. document_version (Optional[str]): Version of the report document, also known as revision. Default is None. issue_date (date): Report issue date in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. contributors (list[ReportContributor]): List of report contributors (e.g. author and verifier) issuing_organisations (list[Organisation]): The organisation(s) issuing the report (e.g. consultant). receiving_organisations (Optional[list[Organisation]]): The organisation(s) receiving the report (e.g. client), if relevant. Default is None. contract_reference (Optional[str]): Reference to contract between the issuing and receiving organisations that governs the energy yield assessment. Default is None. confidentiality_classification (Optional[str]): Confidentiality classification of the report. Default is None. coordinate_reference_system (CoordinateReferenceSystem): Coordinate reference system used for all location data. measurement_stations (Optional[list[MeasurementStationMetadata]]): List of measurement station metadata JSON document(s) according to the IEA Task 43 WRA Data Model, for all station datasets used in the EYA. Default is None. reference_wind_farms (Optional[list[ReferenceWindFarm]]): List of reference operational wind farms used in the EYA. Default is None. reference_meteorological_datasets (Optional[list[ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset]]): List of reference meteorological datasets used in the EYA. Default is None. wind_resource_assessments (Optional[list[WindResourceAssessment]]): List of wind resource assessments, including results, at the measurement station locations. Default is None. turbine_models (Optional[list[TurbineModel]]): List of wind turbine model specifications. Default is None. scenarios (Optional[list[Scenario]]): List of energy yield assessment scenarios. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_met_data.ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset
Metadata for a reference meteorological dataset.
The schema describes a dataset at a single horizontal spatial location. Separate data model instances need to be used to describe data at different location from the same source dataset (e.g. different grid cells from a reanalysis dataset).
Attributes: reference_meteorological_dataset_id (str): Unique ID for the reference meteorological dataset within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the meteorological data.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarm
Reference wind farm metadata.
Attributes: reference_wind_farm_id (str): Unique ID for the reference wind farm within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_farm_configuration (WindFarmConfiguration): The configuration data for the reference wind farm. datasets (list[ReferenceWindFarmDataset]): Metadata for the operational dataset.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.Organisation
Issuing or receiving organisation of an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Entity name of the organisation. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Abbreviated name of the organisation. Default is None. address (Optional[str]): Address of the organisation. Default is None. contact_name (Optional[str]): Name(s) of contact person(s) in the organisation. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.ReportContributor
Contributor to an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the contributor. email_address (Optional[EmailStr]): Email address of the contributor. Default is None. contributor_type (ReportContributorType(StrEnum)): Type of contributor. contribution_comments (Optional[str]): Comments to clarify contribution. Default is None. completion_date (Optional[date]): Contribution completion date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.CoordinateReferenceSystem
Specification of a coordinate reference system for GIS data.
Attributes: system_label (str): Label of the coordinate system. epsg_srid (Optional[int]): EPSG Spatial Reference System Identifier (SRID). Default is None. wkt (Optional[str]): Well-known text (WKT) string definition of the coordinate system. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.turbine_model.TurbineModel
Specification of a wind turbine model.
Attributes: turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. label (str): Label of the turbine model. perf_spec_ref (Optional[TurbineModelSpecification]): Reference to a json document with turbine model performance specification (PLACEHOLDER). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id (str): Unique ID of the wind resource assessment within the EYA DEF document. wind_speed_results (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates from the wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
